        {
            "name": "Dero Stalker",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [],
            "text": "Dero stalkers are those charged with exploring the surface world by night and seeking out new victims to abduct.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Humanoid</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"14\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Society</a></u>)</b>: DC 16",
            "source": {
